platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 小朋友學編碼，自創益智遊戲

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: 這個 App 採用色彩繽紛的易用介面，讓你在製作遊戲時享受如同玩遊戲一樣的樂趣。小朋友 (和成年人) 可以製作各種 App，然後分享創作，以便與其他人一同暢玩。

With its colourful, friendly interface this app lets you have as much fun making games as playing them. Kids (and grown-ups!) can build all kinds of apps, and then share creations so others can play them too.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Little ones can learn to code and make their own games.
